@{b}<< @{u}ScreamerII@{uu} Authors >>@{ub}

@{u}Ray Darrah@{uu} is a software engineer who's job has him coding for the world's most disgusting computer system: the IBM-PC/AT running MS-DOS/LoseBlows. Following his purchase of one of the original A1000's in 1986, Ray's one computing love has always been the true 32-bit @{b}real multitasking@{ub} system known as AmigaOS.

